# 9. 獅子舞ロボ捕獲大作戦！

Tsukasa: Heeelp!
Lion Dance Robot: GROOOAR! CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!
Emu: Wow, Lion Dance Robot's so fast! I wanna chase it too!!
Miku: Oh, me too! If you're having a race, let me join!
Rui: Ah, I think I understand what happened...
Rui: The impact from the mallet must've triggered the self-defense mechanism from the Robo-Nene OS, so it now sees Tsukasa as a threat...
Rui: This is an incredible development! I need to record as much data as I can!
MEIKO: Everyone's having so much fun! Let me join in too♪
Nene: You're kicking up clouds of dust. Could you settle down until we're done here?
Tsukasa: Nooo! You guys! Hurry up and help meee!!!
Len: Wh-What do we do, KAITO? Tsukasa's really in trouble...!
KAITO: Yes. We should save him...! But can we really stop that thing...?
Miku: Stop... Or capture? Because I've got just the thing in that case!
MEIKO: Is that... The giant net you found the other day?
Miku: Yup! I thought we could use it for a sports-themed show or something!
KAITO: Yes, I see. It's big enough to use to catch the Lion Dance Robot.
Miku: Yeah☆ We can do it if we work together!
Len: I'll go and ask Emu and the others to come help too!
Len: So our plan is to capture the Lion Dance Robot using a giant net!
Rui: A terrific plan. I did want to capture some more data but...
Nene: Tsukasa's legs might give out soon if we don't help him...
Emu: I want to help too of course!
Len: Thanks, everyone! Okay, KAITO and Miku will give us the signal and...
Len: Everyone knows what to do, right?
Emu: Yup!
KAITO: Miku, Len, MEIKO, are you ready?
Miku: Yup! All good here!
Len: Me too!
MEIKO: I'm ready too! This should be fun!
KAITO: Okay! Let's begin Operation Lion Capture!
Len & MEIKO: Yeah!
Nene: Okay, Miku's team opened the net... Emu, your turn.
Emu: Yeeeah! I just have to lure the robot into the net, right?
Emu: Easy peasy!
Emu: Yoohoo, Lion Dance Robot! Over heeere!
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP?
Tsukasa: Wait, Emu?!
Emu: Come chase me!
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!!!
Emu: Hahaha! You're so fast! But I'm faster! Catch me if you can!
Rui: Okay. All proceeding according to plan.
KAITO: How did you know the robot would change targets and chase Emu instead?
Rui: The lion from the lion dance is traditionally a bringer of happiness and wards off misfortune.
Rui: So based on that, it's not unlike Emu.
KAITO: Okay...?
Nene: Wait. That sounds more like when dogs at a park start playing with each other...
Rui: Well, yes. You could put it that way too. Oh, Nene. It's almost your turn. Ready?
Nene: Common sense really doesn't apply to you and Emu... Anyways, I'm ready to fly the drone.
MEIKO: I'm ready too!
Nene: Okay, let's raise the net.
Tsukasa: Are those... Rui's drones? Lifting up a huge net...?
Len: Emu! Time for the finale!
Emu: Yeeeah! I'm on it! Running towards the net now☆
Lion Dance Robot: RAAARGH! CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!
Emu: Sorry, Lion Dance Robot! This is the end of our race!
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP...?
Miku: Neneee, now! Release the net!
Nene: Dropping the net on the robot...!
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP CHOMP?!?!
MEIKO: Bullseye! Len, hold down the edge of the net so it doesn't escape!
Len: Roger!
Tsukasa: Nice! They caught it with the net!
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!!!
Rui: We're almost finished. Nene, the rest is up to you.
Nene: Right!
Rui: Lift it up, nice and steady.
Lion Dance Robot: RAAARGH! CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!!
Emu: Woooow, it's being airlifted! Rui's drones are crazy strong!
MEIKO: That's a big catch, huh?
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP...!!!
Rui: Sorry, but it's time to turn you off.
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP?! CH...OM... P...
Len: Phew... I'm glad you're still in one piece, Tsukasa!
Tsukasa: Thanks for helping me out there!
Miku: Welcome back, Tsukasa☆ You must be exhausted after all that running!!
Rui: Hehe. I managed to collect some very interesting data too. Now, I just have to analyze it when I get home.
Tsukasa: Hey, how about showing me some more sympathy? I had an awful time because of your robot, Rui!
Nene: Okay, we get it. You had a rough time. Can we get back to making mochi already...?
Emu: Yeah, let's do it! I brought soy sauce, sweet soybean powder and matcha, so we can make a bunch of different flavors☆
Len: Hey, Emu! Can I have a turn with the mallet?
Emu: Sure! I'll show you how to do it!
Tsukasa: ...
Tsukasa: I feel like they're treating me worse and worse as time passes...
KAITO: What a rough way to start the new year, Tsukasa. I'm glad you're okay.
Tsukasa: It really is and I'm glad SOMEONE acknowledges that.
KAITO: Yes, well...
KAITO: At least you never get bored in this company?
Tsukasa: Yes, that's true!
Tsukasa: Boredom doesn't suit a future star like myself!
KAITO: Hehe. There's our usual Tsukasa.
KAITO: Shall we join the others and make some mochi?
Tsukasa: Right. I'll make mochi with a real bite to it and show off my star power!
